Popular Nigerian singer, Oladapo Daniel Oyebanjo, known by his stage name D’banj and his wife, Lineo Didi Kilgrow are expecting a baby boy in few months time. D’banj said he was broke and received a therapy after loosing his one-year-old son, Daniel jnr who drowned in a swimming pool in his Ikoyi, Lagos home. CONGRATULATIONS TO D’banj!!! He said: “I wanna thank you and everyone out there that has supported. In everything we need to give thanks to God. To lose a child is not something you think about and i have never thought about it before. Am proud to say that in a few months time am going to be a father again.